# The event is typed cg:SpatialEvent but no cg:spatialContext is present.
# The sh:if test matches (the node is a SpatialEvent), so sh:then fires and
# requires cg:spatialContext; it is absent → violation.
# ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

ex:Event-NC04  a cg:SpatialEvent ;

